WEBVTT

00:00.715 --> 00:07.890
When politicians insult Muslims, whether abroad or our fellow citizens,...

00:11.327 --> 00:16.397
...when a mosque is vandalized, or a kid is called names,...

00:18.040 --> 00:19.356
...it doesn't make us safer.

00:20.786 --> 00:23.780
That's not telling it like it is.

00:26.609 --> 00:27.697
It's just wrong.

00:28.541 --> 00:30.925
It diminishes us in the eyes of the world.

00:31.997 --> 00:34.843
It makes it harder to achieve our goals.

00:35.517 --> 00:38.539
It betrays who we are as a country.

